<h2 id='panel'>Panel</h2>
<p>This is a titled Panel component which can be collapsed, it is the default <code>containerComponent</code> used by our filter components</p>

<p><img src="./assets/panel.png" height="150px"/></p>
<pre class="highlight jsx tab-jsx"><code><span class="kr">import</span>  <span class="p">{</span><span class="nx">Panel</span><span class="p">}</span> <span class="nx">from</span> <span class="s2">"searchkit"</span>

<span class="kr">const</span> <span class="nx">PanelExample</span> <span class="p">()</span><span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">(</span>
  <span class="p">&lt;</span><span class="nc">Panel</span> <span class="na">title=</span><span class="s2">"My Panel"</span> <span class="na">collapsable=</span><span class="si">{</span><span class="kc">true</span><span class="si">}</span> <span class="na">defaultCollapsed=</span><span class="si">{</span><span class="kc">false</span><span class="si">}</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>
    <span class="p">&lt;</span><span class="nt">p</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>my content...<span class="p">&lt;/</span><span class="nt">p</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>
  <span class="p">&lt;/</span><span class="nc">Panel</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>
<span class="p">)</span>

</code></pre><h3 id='props'>Props</h3>
<ul>
<li><code>title</code> <em>(string)</em>  - the title of the panel</li>
<li><code>collapsable</code> <em>(boolean)</em> - Whether the panel can be collapsed (defaults to false)</li>
<li><code>defaultCollapsed</code> <em>(boolean)</em> - Whether the panel can be collapsed (defaults to true when collapsable = true)</li>
</ul>
